# Persistent Work Logging

- Maintain a project log in `logs/work-log.md`.
- For each work session, append:
  - timestamp,
  - objective,
  - actions performed,
  - files changed,
  - verification status,
  - blockers or follow-ups.
- Update the log before ending substantial work.
- Prefer short, factual entries over long narratives.
